latestPosts.caption:
📍Hong Island, Krabi 🏝️- The Hong Island is very beautiful with white powdery sand and limestone cliffs spotting the beach making it very photo worthy.
.
.
There is a small shack offering drinks & fruits, so if you are planning to visit, do carry food with you! 🍔🍕
.
.
How to reach? - Take a long tail or speedboat ride from Krabi. 
.
.
Hong Island can be visited as part of Hong Island tour which also includes Pakbia Island, Lao Lading island & Hong Lagoon as well! 🏝️🐠
